### Get all books
GET http://localhost:5000/
# ✅ Example Response (200):
# {
#   "1": {
#     "author": "Chinua Achebe",
#     "title": "Things Fall Apart",
#     "reviews": {}
#   },
#   "2": { ... }
# }

---

### Register a new user
POST http://localhost:5000/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "alice",
  "password": "12345"
}
# ✅ Example Response (201):
# { "message": "User registered successfully." }
#
# ❌ If user already exists:
# { "message": "Username already exists." }

---

### Login as registered user
POST http://localhost:5000/customer/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "alice",
  "password": "12345"
}
# ✅ Example Response (200):
# "User successfully logged in"
#
# ❌ Wrong credentials:
# { "message": "Invalid Login. Check username and password" }

---

### Add a review for a book (ISBN = 1)
PUT http://localhost:5000/customer/auth/review/1?review=Great+book!
# ✅ Example Response (200):
# { "message": "Review for ISBN 1 successfully added/modified." }

---

### Delete the review for ISBN = 1
DELETE http://localhost:5000/customer/auth/review/1
# ✅ Example Response (200):
# { "message": "Review for ISBN 1 by user alice successfully deleted." }
#
# ❌ If review doesn’t exist:
# { "message": "Review not found for this user." }

---

